</section>
<section xml:id="sec-simplify-superposition-visual">
    <title>Simplification Rules for Visualized States</title>

     <sidebyside widths="80% 10%" valign="top">
  
    <p> Once you have completed the calculation, just like in algebra, you need
to inspect the result to see if there are simplifications you can perform. For example, if you have a 
two-qubit system and the result is like the picture to the right, there are a number of steps you can take 
to simplify it. 
</p>
     
